# Enforce LF in the repo on all platforms. Line endings in working copies
# can vary (Git may convert to CRLF on Windows checkout depending on
# autocrlf), but the stored form is always LF — avoids noisy diffs when
# Mac / Linux / Windows collaborators push to the same branch.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Preserve binary / image files as-is.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
